107	              rel="noopener noreferrer"
108	            >
109	              link
110	            </a>{' '}
111	            to create a <b>classic</b> token with <b>repo</b> &{' '}
112	            <b>admin:repo_hook</b> scopes and give your token an expiration, i.e
113	            30d.
